01:22:28.511 --> 01:22:30.580
<i>Well, I don't understand, but I accept it.</i>

01:22:30.680 --> 01:22:33.783
<i>I'm so glad we had this time together.</i>

01:22:33.883 --> 01:22:38.705
<i>I don't think I ever felt
love like this was.</i>

01:22:43.226 --> 01:22:46.763
<i>Maybe someday we'll meet again
under better circumstances.</i>

01:22:46.863 --> 01:22:51.906
<i>Love, Lisa "Anomalisa" Hesselman.</i>

