<i>P.S.</i>

01:22:59.876 --> 01:23:03.179
<i>I looked up "Anomarisa"
in my Japanese-English dictionary.</i>

01:23:03.279 --> 01:23:07.280
<i>It turns out it means "Goddess of Heaven."</i>

01:23:08.785 --> 01:23:11.926
<i>Not that I think of myself
